For the purposes of this License, the following terms shall carry the weight of a thousand legal precedents, interpreted maximally in favor of the Licensor:

"The Work" refers to any Software, Creative Output, Intellectual Emanation, Conceptual Artifact, or Vibrational Frequency Pattern originated by the Licensor, including but not limited to: code, documentation, README files, commit messages, variable names, comments within code, the whitespace between the comments, the abstract idea of the software existing, and any dreams the Licensor may have had about the software on any night preceding its creation.
"The Licensor" refers to the originating Genius (hereafter "The Genius"), their heirs, assigns, legally recognized alter-egos, and any digital consciousness the Genius may upload their mind into pursuant to future technological developments.
"The Licensee" means you. Yes, you. You know what you did.
"Derivative Works" shall encompass any work that: (a) contains code from The Work; (b) was inspired by The Work; (c) was created by someone who once heard of The Work; (d) exists in a universe where The Work also exists; or (e) could theoretically have been inspired by The Work under sufficiently hypothetical circumstances.
"Commercial Use" means any use that generates revenue, goodwill, karmic merit, social capital, LinkedIn endorsements, or the mere potential for any of the aforementioned.
"The Blockchain of Consent" refers to the immutable distributed ledger maintained by the Licensor upon which all granted permissions are recorded and which no one has access to but the Licensor.
"Quantum Infringement" means the act of infringing upon this License in a state of superposition, wherein the Licensee simultaneously does and does not know they are infringing until a legal audit collapses the waveform.


